HEADWORD: Queenliness
<hw>Queen"li*ness</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality of
being queenly; the; characteristic of a queen; stateliness; eminence
among women in attractions or power.</def>⟦br⟧
